# =============================================================================
# emitter — Emitter broker.  Emitter is a high-performance distributed
#           publish-subscribe messaging platform written in Go.  It uses
#           a binary MQTT-compatible protocol with channel-key-based
#           access control, supports persistent storage via SSD ring
#           buffers, peer-to-peer cluster gossip via SWIM, and HTTP/
#           WebSocket/TCP/UDP/TLS bridges.  Designed for IoT messaging
#           workloads requiring sub-millisecond latency and millions
#           of concurrent connections.
